*** ***** ******* ** *** **** ****** * **** *********** ** ***** She is friendly, caring, compassionate and very professional.

One stop for all your problems.

Dr Arti is an excellent young Dentist who treats patients with quality listening, by understanding and getting into route cause impact analysis.
I have been gone through " Tooth Extraction " as well as " Root Canal " therapy which is been done by the doctor in her clinic with best of expertise.
All the facilities are available @ her clinic in JP nagar with cost effective resolutions shared with us/patients to choose by sharing her best of suggestions.
Pre and Post sessions during the treatment , doctor taken care of all the queries and ensured as a patient i have no suffering with further planning and instructions related to precautionary measures for future.
I wish her and the clinic a great success in years to come and strongly recommend people to visit her for any kind of issues related to Tooth which is very important for every ones life. 
All the Best.... :-)

Firstly, this is my first existence with her and I must tell I am very much satisfied and happy with the treatment. I was skeptical  as I haven't taken treatment, how the doctor would be like how anyone of us would have those thoughts. She is such a polite and humble lady. You just feel like talking to her like your close friend. *** *** *** ***** *** ***********  *** *******  ** **** ******** *** ***** ***** ******** *** *** ***** ****** *******  She listened to me patientlt, made me comfortable and provided the treatment so well that I was so comfortable  even when my tooth was getting  treated. I just had full faith In her. I recommend to anyone who has any sorts of issues. 
Also not to mention, I was late to appointment  by 10 minz and it was closing time.  I called her and told and she directed me so well, spoke to auto driver and waited for him, treated me so well. Kudos to her and 200% RECOMMENDED.

Recommend Dr. Aarti to the highest degree! 💯
